{"tid":2004123,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"金像獎內幕:《少年的你》曾向金像獎評審放映加長版足本","createTime":"2020-05-06T08:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T12:23:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b74d24c6fd5c1a8183ab1c7bd2e326de99889a08","tid":2004123,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"香港戲院上映閹割版.<br />\n但行內人(即係金像獎評審)可以睇到加長版足本.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rrroundmidnight/posts/612981569302090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frrroundmidnight%2Fposts%2F612981569302090&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=e05008ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rrroundmidnight/posts/612981569302090</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n午夜翻牆<br />\n53分鐘 &middot; <br />\n【簡簡簡評第39屆香港電影金像獎】<br />\n....<br />\n<strong>小道消息說，《少年的你》曾在香港辦過私人放映，Book了場給行內人特別是大老闆們看，但放映的不是公映（被中國電檢處閹割了幾遍）的版本，因此口耳相傳下，行內反應會比我看到的好（本人沒有機會看過這導演版）。因此導演本人是重視香港（電影）人的評價的。</strong>"},{"pid":"d3c480c7cb1ea66170e314b6f9cdae5da8fe0cd6","tid":2004123,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"走法律罅?"},{"pid":"70ac7ee0ee2a9b6b421b13ce2772a71fec90ccfa","tid":2004123,"uid":202362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5dbf0b293c82ccbbd1cc88044c59065cb57379","tid":2004123,"uid":33614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"算唔算違規？"},{"pid":"730b65d55b7938273797a70161d424721b51b4b5","tid":2004123,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c5